# Static images

**Canonical doc:** [docs/conventions/assets/static-images.md](../../docs/conventions/assets/static-images.md)

Do not use string paths like `"/tenants/logos/foo.png"` for bundled UI images — use static imports under `src/assets/` and `StaticImageData` with `next/image`. For demo content images use `demoContentImageUrl(seed, w, h)` from `@/lib/demo-content-image` (Unsplash CDN); for avatars use `i.pravatar.cc/<size>?u=<id>` (never `loremflickr.com`). Run `npm run check:static-images` before PR.
